<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="49">H. R. Liang 144</emphasis>
(holotype: BCMM, lost); Chongqing: Wushan, 1000 m, 19 April 1989, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="49">B. L. Guo 89003</emphasis>
(neotype, designated by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-011-9275-y" author="Zhang, YJ" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="29" pageNumber="62" pagination="253 - 262" refId="B40" refString="Zhang, YJ, Wang, Y, Li, XW, Li, JQ, 2011. A taxonomic revision of unifoliolate Chinese Epimedium L. (Berberidaceae). Kew Bulletin 66 (2): 253 - 262, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-011-9275-y" title="A taxonomic revision of unifoliolate Chinese Epimedium L. (Berberidaceae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-011-9275-y" volume="66" year="2011">Zhang et al. 2011</bibRefCitation>
