<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="51">
Key to the species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Berberidaceae" genus="Epimedium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Epimedium" order="Ranunculales" pageId="18" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
